                     <interp inst="t18060416-14-off72" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing on the <rs id="t18060416-14-cd73" type="crimeDate">12th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060416-14-off72 t18060416-14-cd73"></join>, a cash, value 10 s. and twenty gallons of shrub, value 13 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
